title: Rug Dr. Mixing Upholstery
description: Learn what to use and how to clean upholstery.

asset.author: Rug Doctor LLC
asset.description: Learn what to use and how to clean upholstery.

transcripts: The sofa and stair solution is ideal for cleaning upholstery stairs and more. You'll want to make sure your machine is empty of other solutions and that you have the upholstery tool handy. Add 2 cups of upholstery cleaner to 1 gallon of hot water. The sofa and stair solution works by breaking up surface oils and dirt without over wetting the fabric just pour the solution into the rug doctor machine you're ready to clean your upholstery.
